title: League won't start up

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: I have not only deleted League countless times, but I also re-downloaded it just as many times and I am still an amateur, but I know that games are not supposed to pop up with that. (Click link for picture) So could you all help me figure out what is happening because League is a fun game and I wanna get back into it. Thanks!

replies.body: This error doesn't impact the quality of your game files, so reinstalling won't be necessary.  The notification is letting you know that your OS has a security setting that's preventing the patcher from launching.  Go over our [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to resolve this.  Let me know if you have any questions!
